      "created": 1777968649,
      "updated": 1777968649
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a51a000000000024baf5",
      "text": "Wikipedia の構成が面白い[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777968411,
      "updated": 1777968792
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a642000000000024bafd",
      "text": "\tオチだけ引いてきても多分面白くない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
